# Mandatory TSDoc Header

For every created or modified `.ts` or `.tsx` file, ensure the file starts with a TSDoc comment block at the very top of the file.

## Required header format

```typescript
/**
 * @module <ModuleName>
 * @description <Brief description of the module purpose>
 * @packageDocumentation
 *
 */